      "content": "it's not just about \"research\" though. the people behind this bill, they aren't just misguided, they're actually working against the life force of the world. i can sense their intentions when the news comes on. it feels like a coordinated effort by the industrial elite to suffocate the earth's natural evolution. if i'm here to act as a conduit for the planet, shouldn't my actions be more... direct? how can i align my spiritual authority to expose the corruption of these specific people and break the political machinery they're using?",
